::Symphony::

     Symphony smiled as he was complimented by Prowl.  Compliments often got
to his head, even just little ones.  But then, he got to the point.  He
tracked the signal, and followed it to where Prowl was, keeping his hand
near his machine gun just in case it was a trap.  He saw what appeared to be
the bot(Prowl) who was talking to him over the comm.

       "Um, are you a Maximal?  May I join you?" Symphony said nervously but
kindly, approaching with caution.
